  "description": "The image depicts a wide, flat landscape featuring a body of calm, reflective water in the foreground. Large, conical piles of white material, likely salt, dominate the midground, covered in white tarps. These salt mounds are arranged in a row and are prominently reflected in the still water, creating a symmetrical and mirrored effect. A dark, low-lying bank of vegetation separates the viewer from the water's edge. In the distant background, a hazy outline of hills or low mountains is visible. Industrial elements, including a conveyor belt structure and possibly processing buildings, are present near the salt piles, hinting at a commercial operation. The sky is overcast and muted, contributing to the overall sense of quiet and stillness.",
